[3]
Date: Tue 11 Dec 2007
Source: Sahara Samay [edited]
<http://www.saharasamay.com/samayhtml/Articles.aspx?NewsId=90819>


Over 100 alligators have fallen prey to a mysterious disease in
Chambal region here [Etawah], the sources said.

However, the reason behind their sudden deaths could not be ascertained.

A huge population of alligators is found in the Chambal region famous
for its barren topography.

